<span id="freeTextContainer14552975133242402011">I was so impressed by how quickly I was drawn into this book. The details in the narrative made me feel like I was a part of the story. The characters were so well written. It was a pleasure to get to know Marty. I was scared for her well being, and I hurt along with her as I read about the heartbreak she had been through. The mystery was intricate, the suspense was palpable, and the romance was sweet. I highly recommend this book for those who enjoy contemporary romance, mystery, and suspense.<br/><br/>I</span>
